lead_paragraph: D.J. Augustin scored Denver's last eight points of overtime, including two free throws with 0.9 seconds left, and the Nuggets beat the Dallas Mavericks 116-114 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Augustin's Free Throws Lift Nuggets Over Mavs in OT, 116-114
